# Synth-1 Design System

**Source of truth:** `STYLE_GUIDE.md` + `design-system/synth-1-fashion-os/MASTER.md`. Tokens: `src/design/tokens.json`, `design-tokens.json`, `src/design/UI_RULES.md`.

**Layout primitives (dashboard / analytics):** `@/components/design-system` — `PageContainer`, `PageHeader`, `SectionContainer`, `DashboardGrid`, `MetricCard`, `AnalyticsCard`, `WidgetContainer`, `ChartCard`, `HistogramCard` (Recharts), `DataTableContainer`, `FilterToolbar`, `EmptyState`, `LoadingState`, `StatusBadge`. Prefer these over one-off card layouts.

## Tailwind (STYLE_GUIDE — JOOR B2B)

| Use | Class |
|-----|-------|
| Page title | `text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900` |
| Section title | `text-base font-semibold text-slate-900` |
| Block label | `text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500` |
| Body | `text-sm text-slate-600` |
| Caption | `text-xs text-slate-500` |
| Card | `rounded-xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white shadow-sm p-5` |
| Primary btn | `bg-slate-900 text-white hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg` |
| Secondary btn | `border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg` |
| Stat card | `rounded-xl border border-slate-100 p-4` |
| Table container | `rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-x-auto` |
| Input | `rounded-lg border-slate-200 h-11` |

Colors: slate-900 primary, indigo-600 accent. Icons: Lucide only, no emojis. Use `@/components/ui`: SectionHeader, StatCard, WidgetCard, EmptyStateB2B. Drawers: `vaul`. Responsive: `@container` (container-queries).

## Tokens & fonts

- `tokens.json` → Tailwind (bg-canvas, text-primary, accent-primary, etc.)
- Fonts: Fira Sans (body), Fira Code (headings). Layout loads them.
- Stack: Next.js + Tailwind + shadcn. Icons: Lucide.

## Checklist

cursor-pointer on clickables, hover 150–300ms, contrast ≥4.5:1, focus states, responsive 375/768/1024.
